Package com.sebastienguillemin.wswrl.ontology

Class DefaultSWRLAPIOWLOntology

java.lang.Object
com.sebastienguillemin.wswrl.ontology.DefaultSWRLAPIOWLOntology
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyChangeListener, org.swrlapi.core.SWRLAPIOWLOntology
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultWSWRLOntology
public class DefaultSWRLAPIOWLOntology extends Object implements org.swrlapi.core.SWRLAPIOWLOntology, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyChangeListener
This class is the DefaultSWRLAPIOWLOntology from the SWRLAPI. The code is exactly the same. This is used to make the SWRLAPI class public (by default, the class scope is package) in order to extend it with the DefaultWSWRLOntology.
